codes.PEAM: Trade will be partially settled early.
codes.PRUR: Part of the trade will be settled on its original date and the remainder will rollover.
codes.PRUW: Part of the trade will not be settled.
codes.UNWR: Original trade will not settle on its original date, but will be rolled over.
